<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM3.3">
<l>māra ṉārvari veñcilaik kāṭceyyum</l>
<l>pāri ṉāroṭuṅ kūṭuva tillaiyāṉ</l>
<l>āra mārva ṉaraṅka ṉaṉantaṉaṉ</l>
<l>nāra ṇaṉnara kāntakaṉ pittaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There will be no associating, for me, with the people of [this] earth who pay homage</l>
<l rend="indent">to the cruel striped bow of the venerable Kāma.</l>
<l>[I am] the madman of Raṅga, Him with a pearl necklace on the chest, the Infinite One,</l>
<l rend="indent">the good Nārayaṇa, the Destroyer of hell.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
